#: src/appdata/org.gnome.Calendar.metainfo.xml.in.in:14
msgid "Manage your schedule"
msgstr "Taqvimlaringizni boshqaring"

#: src/appdata/org.gnome.Calendar.metainfo.xml.in.in:17
msgid ""
"GNOME Calendar is an elegant tool to help you plan and stay on top of your "
"schedule for upcoming days and weeks, whether your months are filled with "
"meetings and appointments, public events, travel logistics, or other "
"commitments in your life."
msgstr ""
"GNOME Taqvimi - bu sizning oylaringiz uchrashuvlar va uchrashuvlar, ommaviy "
"tadbirlar, sayohat logistikasi yoki hayotingizdagi boshqa majburiyatlarga "
"toʻla boʻladimi, kelgusi kunlar va haftalar uchun rejalaringizni "
"rejalashtirishga yordam beradigan ajoyib vositadir."

#: src/appdata/org.gnome.Calendar.metainfo.xml.in.in:22
msgid ""
"Easily create and manage unlimited calendars and events with GNOME "
"Calendar's infinite scrolling month view, week timetable, and scheduling "
"list view."
msgstr ""
"GNOME Taqvimning cheksiz aylanuvchi oy koʻrinishi, hafta jadvali va "
"rejalashtirish roʻyxati koʻrinishida cheksiz kalendar va tadbirlarni "
"osongina yarating va boshqaring."

#: src/appdata/org.gnome.Calendar.metainfo.xml.in.in:26
msgid ""
"Integrating the latest GNOME technologies and design best practices, GNOME "
"Calendar builds on top of the mature Evolution data server to manage large "
"quantities of events and to provide integration with other applications. You"
" can add calendars from various online calendaring services (like NextCloud,"
" Google Calendar, and CalDAV / WebDAV servers), enabling you to synchronize "
"your events across multiple devices and platforms. GNOME Calendar also "
"supports local and offline calendaring, so you can use it anywhere and "
"anytime while travelling (or after civilization's collapse.)"
msgstr ""
"Eng soʻnggi GNOME texnologiyalari va dizayndagi ilgʻor tajribalarni "
"birlashtirgan holda, GNOME Taqvimi katta hajmdagi voqealarni boshqarish va "
"boshqa ilovalar bilan integratsiyani taʼminlash uchun yetuk Evolution "
"maʼlumotlar serveri ustiga quradi. Siz turli xil onlayn kalendar "
"xizmatlaridan (masalan, NextCloud, Google Calendar va CalDAV / WebDAV "
"serverlari) taqvimlarni qoʻshishingiz mumkin, bu sizga tadbirlaringizni bir "
"nechta qurilmalar va platformalarda sinxronlashtirish imkonini beradi. GNOME"
" Taqvimi mahalliy va oflayn taqvimni ham qoʻllab-quvvatlaydi, shuning uchun "
"siz undan istalgan joyda va istalgan vaqtda sayohat paytida (yoki "
"tsivilizatsiya qulagandan keyin) foydalanishingiz mumkin."

